description: This file declares a mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC service, used for unit testing. It contains mocked methods corresponding to the service's RPC calls.

classes.name: SecureStorageServiceMock
classes.description: A mock class inheriting from the SecureStorageService gRPC service for testing purposes, mocking its RPC methods.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mocked RPC method for retrieving a value from secure storage.

methods.name: UpdateValue
methods.description: Mocked RPC method for updating a value in secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteValue
methods.description: Mocked RPC method for deleting a specific value from secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteAllValues
methods.description: Mocked RPC method for deleting all values in secure storage.

methods.name: SeedValue
methods.description: Mocked RPC method for seeding values in secure storage.
